Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:46.54,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(663,377)}The Beast Explodes!\NBurst, Blow\Nand Break Through!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Beast Explodes!\NBurst, Blow and Break Through!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,be staring at...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's faster than earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The medicine from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there some kind of\Nspecial ingredient in it or something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not... bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving around kind of...\Nmade me feel super weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that... all of a sudden...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really... fall asleep...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for it, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like I was sleeping,\Nbut actually I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Shinobi secret...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy Sensei... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.61,0:04:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy Sensei... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell for it yet again, huh?!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sorely mistaken\Nif you think I'm the kind of person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to sleep spread-eagle\Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? What am I doing\Nin a place like this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just drunk, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If so... I'll send you to another world\Nbefore you can even feel pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NI don't have enough Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As might be expected,\Nthings will get hairy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if I stay in the water any longer\Nwith this wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't it hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was sleeping comfortably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a buzzing, annoying fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Bring it on! Hey c'mon...\NI'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What're... those movements...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As you know, in that technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one gets stronger the more one drinks\Nand the more one gets drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,At the restaurant before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lee mistook it for water\Nand drank a small cup of alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It took Neji and me, the both of us,\Nto finally... be able to overpower Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't restrain him yourself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could overpower him\Nif I was fighting him as an enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.86,0:08:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But well, I couldn't inflict a serious injury\Non my beloved student...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it was\Njust with one small cup, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were to drink\Nan entire bottle of alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An invincible strength, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just after\Nhe got out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How long will his body\Nhold on for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A Drunken Fist User, huh...?\NIt's my first time seeing one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to come...\Nthen I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His attacks are straight as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm enjoying my youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too unorthodox...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of all... he's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in the middle of my youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance of the Camellia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read his movements...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,An attack on me...\NThat's quite some Taijutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My attack ability is bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard that earlier\Nfrom the Clone brat, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll sober you up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... not drunk... or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, I'm a minor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Minors shouldn't drink at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Unorthodox, isn't it...?\NThis is my Kekkei Genkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down... Think of a strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seek... some kind of possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.63,0:13:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph. With that wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he wasn't able\Nto escape very far at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my limit...\NI can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NHe's already caught up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My head's pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's with this wound...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I was drunk, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your appearance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've sobered up...\NThis is my Kekkei Genkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kekkei Genkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My Kekkei Genkai freely controls\Nosteoblastic and osteoclastic cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It even controls the concentration\Nof calcium. It's an ability to form bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, there are over two hundred\Nbones in the human body...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, that's not a set number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But bones are bones, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If they break, they break!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a hardness...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these really human bones...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Larch Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more... you clod.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like the time before with Asuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's probably zero possibility\Nof someone coming to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the point of thinking\Nabout someone helping...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell is moving away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you didn't notice your own smell\Nthat you're routinely used to smelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With that you erased your own smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand well the attributes of scent.\NIt figures why I didn't smell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And... as would be expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it's tough having you guys split up in two\Nto search for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The real deal... is from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My role now is to stall this person\Nas long as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I should've avoided a big technique\Nthat could be self-defeating...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems this isn't an opponent\Neasy enough to be able to beat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,without using my Secret Technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had surgery\Nand am not at my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it'd just be opening the first of the\NEight lnner Gates, The Gate of Opening,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I should somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The first gate... Gate of Opening...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Primary Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The impact of the kick\Nwas suppressed by the bones...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some speed... But it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... No matter how much I think,\NI can't come up with any good strategies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it... can't hold any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With me right in front of you,\Nyou can't even howl like a loser...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mine!
